properties.Name: CostItemAggregatedLedgerAccount
properties.Description:
Each cost item associated with a budget may contain values that are aggregates of the values for one or more ledger accounts. 

The ledger accounts that are aggregated for cost item are documented here.

Columns.Name: CostItemId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Cost Item.

Columns.Name: LedgerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Ledger.

Columns.Name: LedgerAccountNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Ledger Account.

Columns.Name: CostItemAggregatedLedgerAccountNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the aggregation of the ledger account for the cost item.
